<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">11</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>Your doctor may recommend the following treatment if you have eczema:</h2></div></div>
